---
title: Mustard Seed Pork Schnitzels with Mumbai Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Pork schnitzel is beloved by all, but we’re putting a twist on it that we think everyone will love. A crispy crumb is a
must for any schnitzel but with a sprinkling of mustard seeds the flavour will burst in your mouth. Even the roasted
veggies are getting something special, a rich spice blend roasted on top. Go ahead and take a bite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

